		<h5>Contrato Para la Formación y el Aprendizaje - Contract for Training and Learning</h5>
		<p>This type of contract is solely used in the event of a company taking on an employee to learn and improve a particular skillset. There are strict laws that severely limit as to who and how they can employ under this type of contract.</p>
