		<h5>Contrato en Prácticas - Internship Contract</h5>
		<p>Interns that work for a company under this type of contract must do so within the first 5 years of graduating and are generally and legally paid less than than the minimum wage. It is forbidden that these type of contracts are of a duration longer than 2 years.</p>
